  <prompt>Implement node executor that calls MembershipResolverService IN-PROCESS (NOT HTTP round-trip) per spec.md FR-1B.1. Reads node config (entityType, roles, outputVariable); binds resolved IDs to OutputVariable for downstream nodes.</prompt>
  <goal>Node executor registered + handles ActionType=52. Configuration validation per node-executor pattern. Tests cover happy path + invalid config.</goal>
  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-013">Extend existing node executor framework</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-010">DI: Singleton executor depending on Scoped MembershipResolverService → use IServiceProvider.CreateScope() pattern (see AgentServiceNodeExecutor for reference)</constraint>
    <constraint source="bff-extensions.md §A">BFF pre-merge checklist</constraint>
  </constraints>
