  <steps>
    <step order="0">Context check + FR-1B.1</step>
    <step order="1">Author LookupUserMembershipNodeExecutor : INodeExecutor (SupportedActionTypes = [LookupUserMembership])</step>
    <step order="2">Implement Validate(): require entityType + outputVariable; roles optional</step>
    <step order="3">Implement ExecuteAsync(): CreateScope per execution → resolve IMembershipResolverService → invoke ResolveAsync → bind to NodeOutput</step>
    <step order="4">Register in NodeExecutorRegistry</step>
    <step order="5">Unit tests: validate path, execute path, missing entityType error, missing OutputVariable error</step>
    <step order="6">Integration test: end-to-end playbook with LookupUserMembership node + downstream consumer of OutputVariable</step>
  </steps>
